<b>Saraswati Sishu Vidya Mandir</b> was established on 1993 at Niladri Vihar, Bhubaneswar.
It is affiliated by Shiksha Vikash Samiti Odisha. 
In a short span of 21 years our School has earned a reputation for itself by creating
pioneering and innovative educational opportunities, teaching & learning practices that
 focus on both curricular and extracurricular activities.

SSVM is progressive, innovative Govt. recognized, Co-educational and Unaided Institution
 which offers a child-centric and activity-curriculum. It provides education from 
 primary classes to standard X according to BSE curriculum. 
 The school follows syllabus prescribed by BSE(Board of Secondary Education). 
 The School offers ample opportunities to the pupils to engage themselves in a wide variety
 of activities, which serve a CHANNELISE STUDENTS EMOTIONAL AND PHYSICAL ENERGY.

